<h3><span id="Enjoy_old-fashioned_games_at_Osakaya"><strong>Enjoy old-fashioned games at Osakaya.</strong></span></h3>
<p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3811" src="https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image28.jpg" alt="ikaho-onsen-ishidangai" width="591" height="443" srcset="https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image28.jpg 591w, https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image28-300x225.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 591px) 100vw, 591px" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">After filling our stomachs, it was time for some fun at Osakaya. At Osakaya, you can try your hand at target shooting under the guidance of an old lady who is very good at teaching you how to do it.</span></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-3815" src="https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image29.jpg" alt="ikaho-onsen-ishidangai" width="591" height="443" srcset="https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image29.jpg 1301w, https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image29-300x225.jpg 300w, https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image29-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image29-768x576.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 591px) 100vw, 591px" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">It was my first time playing the target shooting game, but thanks to the staff’ss instructions, I hit the target on the first shot. I was able to hit three out of ten targets, even the big ones that were difficult to hit! The indescribable feeling I got when I hit the target made me want to try 10 more shots.</span></p>
