<h3><span id="Introduction_of_Ikaho8217s_famous_Yunohana_Manju"><b>Introduction of Ikaho&#8217;s famous Yunohana Manju.</b></span></h3>
<p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3911" src="https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image31-e1646197541857.jpg" alt="ikaho-onsen-ishidangai" width="591" height="395"></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Ikaho Onsen is said to be the birthplace of the onsen manju. Therefore, you can see the word manju everywhere, even on the stone steps. However, the taste of manju can also change depending on the shop.</span></p>

		<style type="text/css">
			#gallery-2 {
				margin: auto;
			}
			#gallery-2 .gallery-item {
				float: left;
				margin-top: 10px;
