			</dt></dl><br style="clear: both" />
		</div>

<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">So on this day, I decided to compare the manju of two stores. I ate the manju from Shingetsu-do (left) and the original Tanaka-ya (right).</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">I was amazed at the difference in taste and texture, as well as the difference in appearance! The Shingetsu-do was fluffy and fluffy, while the Tanaka-ya was moist and chewy. How do you feel about this?</span></p>
